Total Volume Sheet 10

1. Right Click the Sales Select Duplicate . Rename the Sheet as AvgPrice Delete the title and remove Volume form Marks card



2. Drag and drop Total Volume to Text under Marks. 


3.  Click on Text and then click on the ellipses and Select the Text  > Font Type Tableau Bold >Font Size :12 Bold >  Alignment :Center .



3.1 select Alignment and select Horizontal Center and Vertical Center. From the menu bar at the top select Entire view form the drop-down list


4. Right click on Total Volume and select Format


5. Go to pane under Default Select Numbers ,Custom Numbers, Decimal Places 0 and Display Units as Millions.


6. Rt click on title and erase everything and enter Total Volume> Tableau Semi bold > Font size 10 > Bold > Align center .


7. From the Menu bar at the top select the option for viewing and from the drop down select Entire View.
